cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition and language modeling.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper focuses on improving speech recognition performance.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of semi-supervised learning methods.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with improving the performance of an AI system.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with code-switching speech recognition in a specific region, which could be considered a social network of language use.
